This software was part of my first College Programming Project in Instituto Superior TÃ©cnico - Lisboa.
It's meant to simulate the work of 1 or more robot vaccums. Whenever a robot runs out of battery it is stopped.

Please make sure you install the next libraries:
sudo apt-get install libsdl2-dev
sudo apt-get install libsdl2-image-dev
sudo apt-get install libsdl2-ttf-dev

To compile use:
gcc functions.c main.c includes.c comments.c -lm -lSDL2 -lSDL2_ttf -lSDL2_image -o iClean

Read the file comments.c before running!

To run use:
./iClean *name_of_the_map_file*


Map files included in Maps folder.

